                        እስመ፡ እግ<sic resp="DR">ዚ</sic>እትነሰ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ማርያም፡</hi> ቅድስት፡ ይእቲ፡ ወትረ፡ በሰማይ፡
                        ወም<del rend="effaced" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ድር<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi>
                     </explicit>

                     <explicit type="supplication" xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus from="53r" to="53v">Fols 53r–53v</locus>በረከተ<supplied resp="DR" reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ጸሎታ፡
