                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa Māryām</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <hi rend="rubric">ሰላም፡ ሰላም፡ ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ሰምኪ፡ ሐ</hi>ዋዝ<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi> እምነ፡ ከልበኔ ወቍስጥ፡ ወእንምነ፡ ሰንበልት፡ ምዑዝ።
                        <hi rend="rubric">ማርያም፡</hi> ድንግል፡ ለባሲተ፡ ዐቢይ፡ ትእዛዝ<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi> ይስቅየኒ፡ ለለጽባሁ፡ ወይነ፡ ፍቅርኪ እዚዝ<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi>
                     ከመ፡ ይሰቅዮ ውኁዝ፡ ለሠናይ፡ እርዝ<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi>
                     </incipit>

                     <explicit type="supplication" xml:lang="gez"><subst><del rend="erasure">
